com.panacea.sdk.web
Class PMLocalBroadcastReceiver

java.lang.Object
  android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      com.panacea.sdk.web.PMLocalBroadcastReceiver

public class PMLocalBroadcastReceiver
extends android.content.BroadcastReceiver

This Local broadcast receiver allows users to register for web service callbacks from PMWebServiceController.

This is done implementing the PMLocalBroadcastReceiver.PMBroadcastListener and by creating an instance of PMLocalBroadcastReceiver in the class that should receive callbacks:

protected PMLocalBroadcastReceiver mReceiver = new PMLocalBroadcastReceiver();

and then registering and unregistering where required:

mReceiver.register(this, this);

mReceiver.unregister(this);

Author:
Cobi Interactive
